article.description: — Orlando Robinson registered 15 points, five assists and three blocks as Fresno State easily beat San Diego 63-43 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Robinson leads Fresno State past San Diego 63-43
article.linkText: Robinson leads Fresno State past San Diego 63-43
article.story: FRESNO, Calif. -- — Orlando Robinson registered 15 points, five assists and three blocks as Fresno State easily beat San Diego 63-43 on Wednesday night. Jordan Campbell had 12 points for Fresno State (6-1), which earned its fourth straight home victory. Anthony Holland added 11 points and eight rebounds. Vladimir Pinchuk had 11 points for the Toreros (4-5). Joey Calcaterra added 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
